# 📊 End-to-End Data Analytics Project

## 📌 Overview
This project focuses on analyzing a sales dataset to extract meaningful business insights using SQL, Python, Excel, and Power BI.

---

## 🛠 Tools & Technologies
- SQL
- Python (Pandas, NumPy)
- Excel
- Power BI

---

## 📂 Dataset
- Source: Sample sales dataset
- Records: 10,000+
- Features: Customer, Sales, Profit, Region, Date

---

## 📊 Key Analysis Performed
- Total Sales & Revenue Analysis
- Top Customers Identification
- Monthly Sales Trends
- Regional Performance Analysis
- Profit Analysis

---

## 📈 Key Insights
- Identified top 5 customers contributing highest revenue
- Found peak sales months and seasonal trends
- Discovered high-performing regions
- Analyzed profit-driving products

